---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="DAOH3">
  <main
    class="relative bg-retroHasher bg-50% bg-fixed bg-[right_top_8rem] bg-no-repeat lg:bg-33%"
  >
    <header
      class="flex-start flex w-full items-center justify-between bg-gradient-to-b from-extraDark px-3 backdrop-blur-md"
    >
      <img class="h-20 w-36" src="/assets/logo.svg" alt="DAOH3" />

      <div class="flex items-center justify-end bg-opacity-50">
        <p class="font-semi-bold hidden text-2xl text-white md:visible">
          Interested?
        </p>
        <button
          class="2 rounded-xl border border-purple-500 py-2 px-1 font-semibold text-purple-500 transition duration-500 ease-in-out hover:bg-purple-500 hover:text-white"
          onclick="location.href='http://she.energy/join'"
          type="button">Join the Discord</button
        >
      </div>
    </header>
    <div class="flex h-screen w-full flex-col justify-around">
      <div
        class="fixed bottom-5 flex w-full flex-2 flex-col items-center justify-center lg:p-5"
      >
        <div>
          <p
            class="top-24 w-full flex-1 p-2 text-center font-sans text-2xl font-bold text-white md:top-36 md:w-[60%] md:p-4 lg:text-4xl xl:text-5xl 2xl:text-6xl"
          >
            🄰-🄳🅁🄸🄽🄺🄸🄽🄶-🄲🄻🅄🄱-🅆🄸🅃🄷-🄰-🅁🅄🄽🄽🄸🄽🄶-🄿🅁🄾🄱🄻🄴🄼
          </p>
        </div>
        <!-- <p class="text-white text-4xl font-semibold">Next Event</p> -->
        <div class="flex flex-2 flex-col gap-3 p-5">
          <div class="flex flex-col justify-around md:flex-row">
            <div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-1">
              <span
                class="text-md text-left font-dmSans font-semibold text-white md:text-xl"
                >When:</span
              >
              <span
                class="text-md text-left font-dmSans font-semibold text-white md:text-xl"
                >March 3 @ 6:00PM</span
              >
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-1">
              <p
                class="text-md text-left font-dmSans font-semibold text-white md:text-xl"
              >
                Where:
              </p>
              <a
                href="https://goo.gl/maps/EvcgT9WV1cjDrjBu7"
                class="font-semibolds text-md text-left font-dmSans text-white underline md:text-xl"
                >Parking Lot of ETH Denver!</a
              >
            </div>
          </div>
          <img
            class="w-[60vw] shadow-lg lg:w-auto"
            src="/assets/ethDenverHash.svg"
            alt="ethDenverHash"
          />
        </div>
        <p
          class="flex-1 text-center font-dmSans text-sm font-semibold text-white md:text-xl lg:px-4"
        >
          It's that time of year, another DAO event! DAO-H3 is invading Denver
          once again! Last year, we did our first DAO sponsored hash at MCON2
          and it was a raging success. DAO virgins and Hash virgins ran through
          the streets of Denver in chili attire, chasing a FREE keg of Raid
          Brood Red Pil beer! This year we managed to acquire 100 lonely tall
          boys (and some crypto bros). I'm sure the hash knows what to do 😉.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div
      class="sticky top-[100vh] rounded-t-3xl bg-background bg-cover backdrop-blur-3xl"
    >
      <div
        class="absolute top-0 left-0 h-full w-full rounded-t-3xl border border-gray-100 bg-gray-800 bg-opacity-10 bg-clip-padding backdrop-blur-lg backdrop-filter"
      >
      </div>
      <p
        class="relative pt-24 pb-10 text-center text-4xl font-bold text-white lg:text-6xl"
      >
        What Beer Are We Drinking?
      </p>
      <div
        class="relative flex w-full flex-col items-center justify-around gap-3 px-[5%] pb-20 text-center md:px-[25%] lg:flex-row lg:px-[30%]"
      >
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-around">
          <div
            class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-3 rounded-xl border border-white bg-gray-300 bg-opacity-30 p-2 backdrop-blur-md lg:p-4"
          >
            <div class="flex w-full flex-row items-center justify-between p-2">
              <img
                class="color-white top-4 left-5 h-12 w-12"
                src="/assets/beer.svg "
              />
              <a
                class="top-4 right-5 text-center font-sans text-4xl text-white"
                href="https://brood.raidguild.org/redpil">→</a
              >
            </div>
            <p
              class="font-uncial text-2xl font-semibold text-white lg:text-3xl"
            >
              Red Pil - STRAW BLOND KVEIK ALE
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-row items-center justify-center">
              <div class="flex-2">
                <p class="text-center font-sans text-xl text-white">
                  Crisp and dry, traditional pilsner profile with a touch of
                  lemongrass, bergamot and blacktea from late Saphir hop
                  additions. Fermented with OldWorld+NewBeast Kveik Yeast. All
                  the clean pilsner taste, with only 1/6 the brewing time.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="flex flex-1 flex-row justify-center">
                <div>
                  <p class="font-dmSans text-3xl text-white">ABV</p>
                  <p class="font-dmSans text-3xl text-gray-300">5.1%</p>
                </div>
                <div class="m-1 w-0 self-stretch border border-white"></div>
                <div>
                  <p class="font-dmSans text-3xl text-white">IBU</p>
                  <p class="font-dmSans text-3xl text-gray-300">50</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- <div class="w-full h-56 bg-gradient-to-b from-extraDark to-transparent"> -->
      <!-- </div> -->
      <p
        class="relative pt-24 pb-10 text-center text-4xl font-bold text-white lg:text-6xl"
      >
        What is the DAO in DAOH3?
      </p>

      <div
        class="relative flex w-full flex-col items-center justify-around gap-3 px-[5%] pb-3 text-center md:px-[15%] lg:flex-row lg:px-4"
      >
        <div
          class="flex flex-1 flex-col items-center justify-center gap-3 rounded-xl border border-white bg-gray-300 bg-opacity-30 p-2 backdrop-blur-md lg:p-4"
        >
          <div class="flex w-full flex-row items-center justify-between p-2">
            <img class="color-white h-12 w-12" src="/assets/safe.svg" />
            <a
              class="absolute top-4 right-5 text-center font-sans text-4xl text-white"
              href="https://safe.global/#getting-started">→</a
            >
          </div>
          <p class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white lg:text-3xl">
            Treasury Management
          </p>
          <p class="text-center font-sans text-xl text-white">
            DAOH3 uses a Gnosis Safe to manage the treasury. This allows us to
            securely store and manage our funds in a decentralized manner, with
            multi-signature capabilities and customizable access control. As
            DAOH3 has decided not to wrap the Safe in an unincorporated
            non-profit association in the state of Delaware, this would allow us
            to legally protect our members while providing a formal structure
            for the group's governance and operation. With the Gnosis Safe and
            the non-profit association, we can ensure that all transactions are
            transparent and verifiable on the blockchain, while also minimizing
            the risk of loss or theft. Additionally, this approach would allow
            us to raise funds and solicit donations from supporters, providing
            us with the resources we need to grow the group and continue
            providing unique and exciting experiences for our members.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div
          class="flex w-full flex-1 flex-col items-center justify-center gap-3 self-stretch rounded-xl border border-white bg-gray-300 bg-opacity-30 p-2 backdrop-blur-md lg:p-4"
        >
          <div class="flex w-full flex-row items-center justify-between p-2">
            <img class="color-white h-12 w-12" src="/assets/liability.svg" />
            <a
              class="absolute top-4 right-5 text-center font-sans text-4xl text-white"
              href="/">→</a
            >
          </div>
          <p class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white lg:text-3xl">
            Liability Coverage
          </p>
          <p class="text-center font-sans text-xl text-white">Coming soon</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        class="relative flex w-full flex-col items-center justify-around gap-3 px-[5%] pb-20 text-center md:px-[15%] lg:flex-row lg:px-4"
      >
        <div
          class="flex w-full flex-1 flex-col items-center justify-center gap-3 self-stretch rounded-xl border border-white bg-gray-300 bg-opacity-30 p-2 backdrop-blur-md lg:p-4"
        >
          <div class="flex w-full flex-row items-center justify-between p-2">
            <a
              class="absolute top-4 right-5 text-center font-sans text-4xl text-white"
              href="https://docs.wrappr.wtf/how-to/non-profit/#non-profit">→</a
            >
            <img class="color-white h-12 w-12" src="/assets/donations.svg" />
          </div>
          <p class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white lg:text-3xl">Donations</p>
          <p class="text-center font-sans text-xl text-white">
            As a non-profit association, DAOH3 can raise funds through
            donations, charity runs, merchandise sales, and corporate
            sponsorships. By creating clear rules and guidelines, the group can
            provide assurance to donors that their contributions will be used
            responsibly. DAOH3 can maximize its fundraising efforts by utilizing
            its online presence and engaging with supporters through social
            media, email marketing, and its website. The group can also ensure
            transparency and accountability by providing regular updates on how
            funds are being used and financial statements. Through strategic
            fundraising efforts, DAOH3 can build a strong financial foundation
            for its future growth and success.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div
          class="flex w-full flex-1 flex-col items-center justify-center gap-3 rounded-xl border border-white bg-slate-300 bg-opacity-30 p-2 backdrop-blur-md lg:p-4"
        >
          <div class="flex w-full flex-row items-center justify-between p-2">
            <img class="color-white h-12 w-12" src="/assets/anonymous.svg" />
            <a
              class="absolute top-4 right-5 text-center font-sans text-4xl text-white"
              href="https://docs.wrappr.wtf/how-to/quick-notes/#legality-of-key-signatures"
              >→</a
            >
          </div>
          <p class="text-xl font-semibold text-white lg:text-3xl">Anonymity</p>
          <p class="text-center font-sans text-xl text-white">
            DAOH3, a decentralized autonomous organization (DAO), enables its
            users to retain anonymity by utilizing blockchain technology to
            protect user identities. Unlike traditional organizations, DAOH3
            operates on a peer-to-peer network and does not require personal
            information or identification from its members. Transactions are
            recorded on the blockchain, which ensures transparency and
            immutability while protecting user privacy. Additionally, DAOH3
            allows users to participate and vote on proposals anonymously,
            further protecting their identities. By utilizing these innovative
            technologies, DAOH3 empowers its members to participate in
            decentralized decision-making while preserving their anonymity.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- <div class="h-56 w-full"></div>
      <div class="h-56 w-full"></div>
      <div class="h-56 w-full"></div>
      <div class="h-56 w-full"></div> -->
  </main>

  <style>
    .body {
      background-color: #1d1d1d;
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
